title: David Gilmour - Live in London - 2015-10-03
description:
A fresh bootleg from the recent European tour. Really nice recording.

Enjoy, share and seed please. Check my account for more classic bootlegs.

=========================================================================

Here the first recording for the last date of European Tour.

Many thanks to Leadville200 to share and permission to seed here.
